{"tid":2228091,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駿洋邨入伙再延期　準住戶生活遇困難：長洲坐船出來上學，小朋友捱不住。","createTime":"2020-10-03T09:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T05:14:49.000Z","uid":209657,"like":5,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6f11f7b3a358214817067c95ad32e130a96dc561","tid":2228091,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQB5aIl5Ze55DgML&amp;w=750&amp;h=391&amp;url=fbstaging%3A%2F%2Fgraph.facebook.com%2Fstaging_resources%2FMDExMDM4MDkxMDYzMzA2NzY1Ojk5MDc2NDgzOA%3D%3D&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;_nc_cb=1&amp;_nc_hash=AQDi-5G8RMKFJrcF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQB5aIl5Ze55DgML%26w%3D750%26h%3D391%26url%3Dfbstaging%253A%252F%252Fgraph.facebook.com%252Fstaging_resources%252FMDExMDM4MDkxMDYzMzA2NzY1Ojk5MDc2NDgzOA%253D%253D%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26_nc_cb%3D1%26_nc_hash%3DAQDi-5G8RMKFJrcF&h=4cb2699f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被徵用作檢疫中心的火炭駿洋邨，第一至三座居民可在明年一月入伙。入伙時間一再延期，準住戶在安排子女上學、住屋及生活開支上都遇到困難。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生一家輪候公屋九年，原本這個時候，應已遷入駿洋邨第二座的單位，但遇上疫情，入伙時間一拖再拖，更需搬到酒店暫住，方便小朋友在同區上學。<br />\n<br />\n駿洋邨第二座準居民陳先生：「抽到駿洋邨，所以就轉了這個校網，轉（校網）前政府都不說，明年才可入伙，這樣我失了預算，若我之前知道，我會在長洲讀多一年。若長洲坐船出來要凌晨五時多，出到中環差不多六時，還要坐車進入沙田，若日日這樣，小朋友會捱不住。」<br />\n<br />\n陳先生是物業保養維修技工，一個月薪金只有約兩萬元，酒店租金已用了一半，即使政府已兩次向他們發放六千元特惠津貼，但幫助不大。"},{"pid":"df9d3beabcb33efbf5d214160e8d28ce60ff765f","tid":2228091,"uid":26770,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"捱不住就送保良局"},{"pid":"d3fe9dd20d1334fccefff55f4e54ba584bcc871d","tid":2228091,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2aUpEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2aUpEa.jpg&h=e2da0be3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府現時承諾明年一月可以入伙，他希望再早些。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生：「希望能11月還給我們，因為1月才派鎖匙，2月已新年，我擔心很多裝潢公司都未必能配合，最想是很快裝潢好，家人可以住得舒服。」<br />\n<br />\n入伙日期一拖再拖，陳先生指要等收到鎖匙後，才會安排裝潢和買家具，以免再一次失預算。"},{"pid":"2b35d5451f60a6c00b12d076be8e6bac04fee722","tid":2228091,"uid":85864,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"一手樓變二手樓"},{"pid":"ef1b6b6fe2e0babd99c5d724e88fa85421e6bbb2","tid":2228091,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=407689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407689&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=3db036b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407689&h=c166e25a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=407689</a>"},{"pid":"c5508defd31aa056d1164e59c0a2ad71f7f21c02","tid":2228091,"uid":374134,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T10:24:23.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd6a1003b5aece28ea04ada825241877a9cbb11","tid":2228091,"uid":227275,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d3fe9dd20d1334fccefff55f4e54ba584bcc871d","tid":2228091,"uid":209657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T09:50:34.000Z","msg":